==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Numerosity
<hw>Nu`mer*os"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>numerositas</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state of being
numerous; numerousness.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Rhythm; harmony; flow.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>numerosity</qex> of the sentence pleased the ear.</q>
<rj><qau>S. Parr.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Numerous</ent>⟦br⟧
